These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, fantasy, horror, satire, scientific, superhero
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, juice, milk, fanta, lemonade, water
The people have 7 different jobs:  writer, dancer, social-worker, police-officer, coach, paramedic, engineer
 1. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
 2. the dancer is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the engineer is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the paramedic##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is the engineer##1
 7. the person drinking milk is between the police-officer and the person watching satire movies##2
 8. the coach is on the left of the paramedic##1
 9. the paramedic is on the left of the writer##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is the person drinking juice##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is the person watching horror movies##1
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
13. the writer is the person drinking fanta##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is between the social-worker and the engineer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | comedy     | scientific | disaster | horror | superhero  | fantasy  |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | milk        | soy-milk  | water     | lemonade   | juice       | fanta   |
| Job         | dancer   | engineer | police-officer    | social-worker  | coach | paramedic | writer |

