.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
City: marseilles, colone, new-york, prague, nizza, venice, london
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, handball, parkour, sailing, snowboarding, soccer
7 different games are played: poker, chess, billiard, scrabble, mah-jongg, backgammon, go
 1. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is the person traveling to london##1
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is the person playing scrabble##1
 7. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person playing go##2
 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
11. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
12. the person playing poker is the person traveling to colone##1
13. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
14. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
15. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| City   | venice | london      | prague     | marseilles  | nizza | new-york | colone |
| Sport         | cricket  | badminton | snowboarding | handball | soccer | parkour   | sailing  |
| Game     | billiard   | backgammon     | go        | scrabble  | mah-jongg   | chess       | poker      |

