 2. the person driving the taxi is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is the person traveling to new-york##1
 5. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the van and the person watching mystery movies##2
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
10. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
11. the person driving the roller is the person watching comedy movies##1
12. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
13. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
14. the person driving the van is the person traveling to berlin##1
15. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
