The people prefer 7 different music-genres: punk, gospel, blues, rock, indie, pop, country
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, car, roller, skateboard, taxi, train, tram
 1. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
 2. the person driving the roller is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of pop is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 4. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
 5. the fan of punk is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is the fan of country##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is the person driving the train##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
 9. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person driving the car##1
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the fan of pop##1
11. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the train##1
12. the fan of punk is in the middle##1
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
14. the person driving the skateboard is the fan of rock##1
15. the owner of the horse is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |     5      |     6     |     7      |
| Pet        | dog          | hedgehog | hamster      | horse  | guinea-pig     | rat  | frog |
| Music-Genre       | indie | country   | pop | punk | rock     | blues | gospel |
