 8. the person eating kale is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 9. the coach is the person who's birthday is in december##1
10. the analyst is on the right of the scientist##1
11. the engineer is on the right of the doctor##1
12. the person who's birthday is in july is the analyst##1
13. the architect is in the middle##1
14. the analyst is between the person eating lime and the firefighter##2
15. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
16. the analyst is on the left of the firefighter##1

