 3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the writer##1
 4. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 6. the dressmaker is on the right of the writer##1
 7. the dressmaker is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person watching sports movies##2
