 2. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is the person who likes white##1
 5. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 6. the person who likes apricot is the owner of the cat##1
 7. the owner of the rat is the person who likes mauve##1
 8. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
11. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
12. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
13. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
14. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
15. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who likes blue and the person who's sport is climbing##2

.:: Answer ::.
