.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: january, march, june, september, august, may, july
The people have 7 different hobbies: dancing, filmmaking, gardening, photography, skydiving, traveling, writing
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, baccarat, game, havana, bolivar, cain, vegafina
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 2. the cain-smoker is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
 6. the cain-smoker is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the game-smoker is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 8. the havana-smoker is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the game-smoker##2
 9. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
10. the person who's hobby is photography is in the middle##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
13. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the vegafina-smoker and the person who's hobby is writing##2
15. the vegafina-smoker is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5      |      6      |     7     |
| Birthday   | july  | may   | august   | september        | june     | march | january       |
| Hobby      | dancing | filmmaking | writing | photography | gardening  | skydiving   | traveling |
| Cigar        | vegafina   | baccarat     | tiparillo     | cain      | bolivar | havana    | game      |

 